---
title: Easter Rosemary & Garlic Lamb with Dauphinoise Potatoes with Chocolate Brownies for Dessert
description: Roast a tender and succulent lamb rump that's just right for a small gathering. With all the flavour of traditional roast lamb, plus a decadent potato bake on the side, this meal includes everything you need for a special occasion dinner. And the best meals end with a sweet treat, so we've included double chocolate brownies for dessert!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easter-rosemary-garlic-lamb-17b27d6e.jpg
